data.title: Pi Network Ventures backs OpenMind for developing decentralized OS for robots, using a network of 350k+ nodes.
data.description: Pi Network Ventures has made an investment in OpenMind to aid in the creation of a decentralized operating system for robots. This initiative will involve utilizing a network that consists of more than 350,000 nodes.

data.title: Increase in AI-fueled crypto scams, making detection trickier. Stay informed on latest scams & protect against AI-driven fraud.
data.description: Artificial intelligence is revolutionizing the landscape of crypto scams, leading to increased complexity and difficulty in detection. data.title: Liquor industry embracing digital revolution with technologies like cloud computing, big data, IoT, and AI.
data.description: On October 31, 2025 in Beijing, the liquor industry is experiencing a transformation due to the rise of the digital economy. Advanced digital technologies like cloud computing, big data, the Internet of Things, and artificial intelligence are quickly evolving and becoming closely interconnected within the industry. This integration is reshaping the entire liquor industry chain by utilizing these technologies to enhance efficiency and innovation.

data.title: Primerica HBI™ data shows middle-income purchasing power steady in Sept. HBI™ at 100.4%, up 0.2% from last month and 0.6% from last year.
data.description: In Duluth, Ga., the most recent Primerica Household Budget Index™ (HBI™) data showed a reading of 100.4% for September. This index, which assesses how inflation and wage patterns affect middle-income families' ability to meet daily expenses, has increased by 0.2% from the previous month and 0.6% from last year. The Consumer Price Index (CPI), a gauge of inflation for a wide range of goods for all U.S. households, saw a 3.0% rise in September compared to the previous year.
